  "body": "<p>Hello everyone, my name is Violeta Scrap and today I want to share with you a layout I created using the latest collection by Amy Tangerine, “On a whim”.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/f19fb91f9c7495fd.jpg?v=1782539559\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>On this Layout I used a combination of so many of my favorite things: small pictures, watercolors, a big focal point shape in the background, and a smattering of letters and stickers.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/7b86586f80558875.jpg?v=1782539562\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>So to create this page, I used a few of my favorite papers from “On a whim” to create a coffee cup. Instead of using my Silhouette, I decided to handmake it. I drew the coffee cup on a scrap piece of paper and cut two pieces.</p><p>I picked a piece of white paper and I started building the final page. I placed the coffee cup around the middle and created a small cluster to help my photo pop.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/1d3eb43883a418c8.jpg?v=1782539565\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>I really love mixing different materials so I included clear stickers, Thickers, washi tape, and puffy stickers. I also fussy cut some words from one of apart sheets and used them in the page as ephemera.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/325ce4556215b16a.jpg?v=1782539568\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>My title “awesome” is made using the chipboard from “On a whim” collection. When I was looking through my supplies and I saw this I knew it would be perfect. It complements the colour well and it's the perfect sentiment too.</p><p>I´ve written my journaling with a black pen. I love the look of handmade journaling.</p><p>As a final touch, I added some big splatters in the layout. I used hot pink to keep the colors balanced across the page.</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0981/5667/5392/files/f1173bd622af18ce.jpg?v=1782539570\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>With just a little creativity you can work your Amy Tangerine collections into any layout theme. I really hope you enjoyed this layout and got inspired to create a beautiful page about yourself. Until next time!</p><p>Violeta Scrap</p><p><a href=\"http://violetascrap.com/\">Blog</a> | <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/violeta_scrap/\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.twitter.com/violeta_scrap\">Twitter</a> | <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/VioletaScrap/\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/VioletaScrap\">YouTube</a></p><p>Supplies: On a whim - 12x12 Double Sided Paper - Confetti (378732), On a whim - 12x12 Double Sided Paper - Heaps of love (378736) On a whim - 12x12 Double Sided Paper - All the feels (378728), On a whim - Thickers - LOL (378746), On a whim Collection - Washi Tape Pack (378747), On a whim Collection - Clear Stickers, Oh happy life - Clear Stickers, Oh happy life Collection - Die-cut shapes (376224), Oh happy life Collection - Puffy Stickers (376238), American Crafts - Thickers - White</p><p><em>Thanks so much for sharing this layout, Violeta! Shop ON A WHIM now! Check your local retailer and online at </em><a href=\"http://bit.ly/onawhim\"><em>Simon Says Stamp</em></a><em> and </em><a href=\"http://bit.ly/amytangerineonawhim\"><em>Scrapbook.com</em></a></p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
